title: Between the Bars
lastfmSummary: “Between the Bars” is the fourth track of Elliott Smith’s 1997 album, Either/Or. It is written as a short ballad in the key of G Minor. Possibly Smith’s most popular song, it is one of three tracks from Either/Or that were used in the soundtrack of the film “Good Will Hunting”.
